{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T13:24:16.635Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"custom_tool_call_output","id":"ctco_019f7566-267b-7ae2-b04d-5af4da4327f2","call_id":"call_mGJ9Mk5d6lAG22VOTXKDJtL9","output":[{"type":"input_text","text":"Script completed\nWall time 0.2 seconds\nOutput:\n"},{"type":"input_text","text":"# Compiler-Oracle Agentic Smoke\n\nDevelopment-only; predefined repositories; Claude Opus; exhaustive expectations for the selected compiler-oracle neighborhoods. Exactness is scoped to those compiled neighborhoods.\n\n| System | Exact | Macro recall | Micro recall | Tool calls | Wall time (s) | Provider input incl. cache | Output tokens | Cost (USD) | Compliance |\n| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |\n| file-tools | 0.667 | 1.000 | 1.000 | 10.7 | 82.6 | 371759 | 14581 | 0.9619 | 1.000 |\n| entire-graph | 0.667 | 1.000 | 1.000 | 10.3 | 94.3 | 286523 | 19989 | 1.1360 | 1.000 |\n| cbm | 0.500 | 0.667 | 0.733 | 18.3 | 122.2 | 823393 | 20535 | 1.5839 | 1.000 |\n"}],"internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f7564-f8e8-7981-b0a9-28667898c518"}}}
