{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T14:04:57.685Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","id":"fco_019f758b-65d5-77d0-9108-ace2d2367b4f","call_id":"call_Acgd3a0dxPeVvsD2HX3oKZRP","output":"{\"agents\":[{\"agent_name\":\"/root\",\"agent_status\":\"running\"},{\"agent_name\":\"/root/index_cache\",\"agent_status\":{\"completed\":\"Implemented the query-independent preindex/cache path without committing or pushing.\\n\\nKey outcomes:\\n\\n- Added HEAD-only `entire graph index` with profile/cache options and JSON provenance, counts, warnings, cache-hit, and latency fields.\\n- Explicit preindexing now verifies the cache was durably written.\\n- Selective committed searches reuse compatible full prebuilt snapshots without changing retrieval results.\\n- `--index-all-files` now uses the canonical query-independent cache key.\\n- Cache hits refresh commit provenance when different commits share the same tree.\\n- Added CLI and semantic cache tests, including persistence failures and cached/uncached retrieval parity.\\n\\nFocused tests and vet pass.\"}},{\"agent_name\":\"/root/mirror_dedup\",\"agent_status\":{\"completed\":\"Implemented and integrated semantic mirror deduplication.\\n\\n- Exact symbol mirrors collapse using language, kind, qualified name, signature, and body hash.\\n- Canonical authored paths are preferred using general heuristics.\\n- Explicit path-specific queries retain requested variants.\\n- Distinct tracked `lib/` and `dist/` code remains searchable.\\n- Identifier-usage quotas now prioritize authored paths.\\n- Added unit and end-to-end regression coverage.\\n- Frozen Zod check now returns canonical `src` definition and usages at ranks 1–4.\\n- Full `internal/sem` suite passes in 25.4s.\\n\\nNo commit or push performed.\"}},{\"agent_name\":\"/root/neighbor_efficiency\",\"agent_status\":{\"completed\":\"Implemented neighbor response efficiency and scope changes:\\n\\n- Added JSON `index_cache_hit` and `index_latency_ms`.\\n- Added `--internal-only` and `--exclude-tests`.\\n- Preserved queried focus symbols, production edges, and `CONSTRUCTS` relations.\\n- Filtered dependent two-hop paths automatically.\\n- Replaced Cartesian path enumeration in agent output with one exact caller × focus × callee family.\\n- Added focused coverage in `internal/cli/neighbors_efficiency_test.go`.\\n- Focused tests pass.\\n\\nNo commit or push performed. The root agent was told to add `[--internal-only] [--exclude-tests]` to the concurrently edited help line.\"}}]}","internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f756f-5147-7222-9084-187ed68d3651"}}}
